            <text>
                <body>
                    <div xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xml:lang="nl" type="original">
<pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-orig-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/>

<p xml:id="p.nl.1" n="1">Winschoten<ptr target="#note-t-1"/> 31 Decembre 1888</p>
<space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>

<p xml:id="p.nl.2" n="2">Amice!</p>

<p xml:id="p.nl.3" n="3">In langen tijd heb je niets van mij vernomen. Ik wensch je nu maar bij dezen een gelukkig nieuwjaar en zal spoedig je brief beant<c type="shy">-</c>woorden die ik dezen zomer ontving<c type="kp">_</c><ptr target="#note-t-2"/></p>
<space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>

<p xml:id="p.nl.4" n="4">Adieu<c type="kk">/</c> à bientot</p>

<p xml:id="p.nl.5" n="5">A.H. Koning</p>
    <space unit="lines" quantity="1"/><pb f="1v" n="2" xml:id="pb-orig-1v-2" facs="#zone-pb-1v-2"/></div>

                    <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                        <pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-trans-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/>
<p xml:id="p.en.1" n="1">Winschoten<ptr target="#note-t-1"/> 31 December 1888</p><space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
<p xml:id="p.en.2" n="2">My dear friend!</p>
<p xml:id="p.en.3" n="3">You have heard nothing from me for a long time. Now I wish you herewith a happy New Year, and will shortly reply to your letter that I received this summer.<ptr target="#note-t-2"/></p><space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
<p xml:id="p.en.4" n="4">Adieu, more soon</p>
<p xml:id="p.en.5" n="5"><rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_1145">A.H. Koning</rs></p><pb f="1v" n="2" xml:id="pb-trans-1v-2" facs="#zone-pb-1v-2"/>
                    </div>
