<p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">5-cent postcard. Postmarked on the front: ‘WINSCHOTEN 31 / DEC / 88 <hi rend="italics">[xx]</hi> – 12 N’ and ‘ARRAS A PARIS 2 / JANV / 89’; on the side with the text ‘ARLES BOUCHES DU RHONE 2e | 3 / JANV / 89’. The address reads: ‘Monsieur Vincent van Goch/ n° 2 Place Lamartine/ <hi rend="italics">Arles</hi>./ France./ Bouches du Rhône’.</p>
                                    
                                
                    	</note>
                    
